reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Suits our needs
reviews.reviewText: This lamp is very stylish and easy to put together. We have it behind our accent chair, and between the two it looks really nice in our living room. We have it on a controlled plug so every time we switch it on it it changes the light intensity. I just wish you could change it manually not when you just turned power on and off to it and it would stay at the same intensity all the time
